provided by the New York Institute of Photography Here are some ideas to help you take pictures that capture the essence of the current season winter spring summer or fall Even if youre in a different latitude and your climate is considerably different from ours in New York you may still find valuable tips here Our discussion of a particular picture that we think captures the essence of the current season in the Northern Hemisphere often involves a photographic technique that is basic to good photography in general So whether you live in Australia or Oahu Beijing or Boston check out this page
